，重启之后疯狂同步，因为重启之前 iCloud 实际上没同步好，发生了故障</p>\n<p>macOS 的 bug 真多啊</p>\n", "last_modified": 1679622646, "replies": 118, "id": 926735}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 200085, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 3747, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 515568, "username": "AMZsowhat", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/AMZsowhat", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/afb3/d156/515568_mini.png?m=1676965505", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/afb3/d156/515568_normal.png?m=1676965505", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/afb3/d156/515568_large.png?m=1676965505", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/afb3/d156/515568_xlarge.png?m=1676965505", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/afb3/d156/515568_xlarge.png?m=1676965505", "created": 1604283759, "last_modified": 1676965505}, "last_reply_by": "toomoy", "last_touched": 1679663350, "title": "向广东朋友们求助，如何防治蟑螂？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/926686", "created": 1679586023, "deleted": 0, "content": "北方捞仔来广州打螺丝，最近快到雨季，家里开始有出现一些蟑螂，非常可怕，想请教广东友友们怎么对付！买了胶饵但好像没什么用，门缝下贴了填充泡沫棉条堵上也还是能见到 55555 我真的服了", "content_rendered": "北方捞仔来广州打螺丝，最近快到雨季，家里开始有出现一些蟑螂，非常可怕，想请教广东友友们怎么对付！买了胶饵但好像没什么用，门缝下贴了填充泡沫棉条堵上也还是能见到 55555 我真的服了", "last_modified": 1679586023, "replies": 94, "id": 926686}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1677911181", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1677911181